<taxonomicName id="EA48BF38EEB689D0B95CAB5E9BA91D7A" class="Demospongiae" family="Raspailiidae" genus="Trikentrion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Trikentrion laeve" order="Axinellida" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" phylum="Porifera" rank="species" species="laeve">Trikentrion laeve</taxonomicName>
Carter, 1879, holotype BMNH 1848.10.4.6, A shape of holotype specimen (size bar = 1 cm) B details of apices of long thin style C short thin style C1 detail of rounded head of short thin style D oxeas E polyactine F trichodragma.
</paragraph>
